org.drip.service.bridge

Class CreditAnalyticsRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.drip.service.stream.Serializer
      • org.drip.service.bridge.CreditAnalyticsRequest

  • public class CreditAnalyticsRequest
extends Serializer
    CreditAnalyticsRequest contains the requests for the Credit Analytics server from the client. It contains the following parameters: - The GUID and the time-stamp of the request. - The component that is being valued. - The valuation, the pricer, and the quoting parameters. - The market parameters assembled in the ComponentMarketParams. Typical usage is: Client fills in the entities in the request, serializes them, and sends them to the server, and receives a serialized response back from the server.
